      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The city council will meet tonight\nin committee OF the whole to con\nslider the franchises of the Spokane\nTraction company and tho Washing\nton Water Power company. No de-\ncision is expected TO be reached az\nsome of the councilmen are in favor\nOF waiting until the new members\ntake their seats in May."
